{"build_type":"library","description":"Build-time injector: prepend the self-describe prologue to an entry function's execution_instructions array (ei), embedding contract_text as the compiled-in contract. Parses a fixed 4-instruction template (__dz=0 ; __dc=<contract> ; __dh=emit_contract_text_if_describe_requested(__argc,__argv,__dc) ; if __dh!=__dz return __dz), writes contract_text into the __dc declaration's source_target valuestring, then prepends the four instructions in reverse so final order is __dz,__dc,call,guard,<original...>. Requires the entry to have __argc/__argv params (caller gates on that). Reuses decode_entire_source_building_document, fetch_member_residing_within_sequence, locate_named_member_inside_mapping, field_write, prepend_item_into_array_head.","module_name":"inject-describe-prologue-inside-instruction-sequence","package_name":"inject-describe-prologue-inside-instruction-sequence","function_definitions":{"inject-describe-prologue-inside-instruction-sequence":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"ei","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"contract_text","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"two","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":2},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"three","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":3},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_st","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"source_target"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_template","variable_type":"str","assignment_ope